	nother. \\nJoin us at Brighton Playfield in South Seattle. Map: goo.gl/map
	s/c74cytjrRB1vpT7h7\\nWe almost always play on the most southern edge of t
	he field. \\nWe confirm if we have enough players each Sunday on a sociali
	st soccer Signal chat. To be added\\\, download the Signal app\\\, and ema
	il your phone number to tdupuis42@gmail.com with a request to be added. \\
	nThe game is usually at 10 AM\\\, but that may change\\\, so make sure you
	 are on the Socialist Soccer signal chat!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/
